{"title":"新棉衣","authors":["北方"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":10,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"新棉衣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上级"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给我发下了一套"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"崭新的棉衣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又轻软，又合适"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我把它穿到身上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有着说不出的欢喜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从乡村到城市"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十多年了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一次"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我穿起了这样阔气的棉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"衣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我换下了粗布军装"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我把它包在一个包袱里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要看它质料劣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我对它可挺珍爱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在太行山上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它是我最贴身的伴侣啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它浸满着我的汗渍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"积存着我的荣誉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士的血汗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"换来了中国人民的胜利"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国人民的胜利"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带来了自由和幸福"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——这崭新的棉衣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只是其中一份小小的献"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"礼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要保卫我们的胜利"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保卫我们的国家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保卫我们的毛主席"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远做一个新中国的捍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卫者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"做一个捍卫祖国的铁打"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的战士。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（十月二十五日）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}